Date: Wed, 1 Feb 2006 16:46:33 -0500
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.746.2)
X-OriginalArrivalTime: 01 Feb 2006 21:46:11.0725 (UTC) FILETIME=[EAE7B3D0:01C62778]
X-Spam-Checker-Version: SpamAssassin 3.0.2 (2004-11-16) on 
